parameters: S-Stop... that's... too lewd... please stop.

various items, I'll buy them for you.

Oh, sorry. Because I don't look like a bad
monster, everyone is always surprised.

How unusual, isn't it? A talking monster, then you
must be Pomurin?
Let me run this tool shop, Pomurin.

I'm Konoha, the magical girl. Nice to meet you. I
have a request from Dorothy. I need an antidote
potion for drug addiction. Do you have one?

Eh... an antidote potion... the materials to make
one for addiction are currently out of stock...
what a coincidence... I'm sorry...

I wonder if having the materials would be enough?
I'll go gather them.

If that's the case, it would be a relief. I wrote
down the materials needed, so I can make it right
away if we have the materials.

To obtain the 'Poisonous Mushroom,' you should go
to the hot springs near the castle and collect
some 'Hot Spring Water.' The hot springs are
located to the northwest, so thoroughly
investigate the waterfall in that direction.
Alright, I understand. I'll hurry and gather them.

No problem, with this it will be complete. I'll do
my best.

It's done. With this antidote potion, I'm sure
Lady Rudia will fully recover.

Ah, sorry, it's not like Dorothea got poisoned or
anything. It's just that the surveillance officer
at the observation tower...

It wasn't Lady Dorothea, but if that's the case,
then it's a relief. Lady Dorothea is a vampire, so
I thought it was strange.
S-Stop... that's... too lewd... please stop.

If there's anything you want me to put out, like
various items, I'll buy them for you.

Sorry, but I won't fall for that kind of trap.
I've been caught in the beauty scam a hundred
times, you know.

It is said that magical girls generally do not
die, but on the flip side, it means they will
suffer for eternity. So, they must be careful not
to become a breeding ground for demons or anything
like that.
